    <item>
      <title>加拿大的美元在动荡的，贸易燃料的会议上上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/canadian-dollar-slumps-as-trump-threatens-to-double-steel-levies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大的美元在一次动荡的会议上上升，该会议看到贸易战风险激增，然后在周三的加拿大银行会议之前退缩，当时决策者有望降低利率，以避免美国税的经济威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/canadian-dollar-slumps-as-trump-threatens-to-double-steel-levies</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 14:58:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于指标信号下降过度，石油从六个月低点上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-11</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于内部市场指标闪烁了最近下降的迹象，石油越来越遥遥无期，这使乌克兰暂时停战的前景掩盖了越来越多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-11</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 23:25:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着特朗普看涨增长：市场包裹，股票在很晚的时间内增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，他看不到经济衰退，在他的贸易战争中轻描淡写，股票在末日攀升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
